            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The direct registration of protons.",
                "The differential cross sections of the reaction",
                " gd -> pn were calculated using the relation (2) of",
                " the article: dSIG/dOMEGA = (A/NP)(C/J) where",
                " N is the Avogadro number, A and p are atomic weight",
                " and density of the target, C is the yield of the",
                " reaction, and J is the integral over the angular and",
                " energy acceptance of the experimental arrangement",
                " and the effective volume of the target formed by the",
                " intersection of the incident photons with the",
                " deuterium target. The integral was calculated by the",
                " Monte Carlo method."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The mean-root-square errors are given."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-SYS",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The systematic ones were estimated to be",
                " about 4.4 % as determined by the following factors:",
                " the photon-beam monitoring (1.5%), the number of",
                " atoms in the deuterium target (1%), and the geometry",
                " of the experiment (the size of the beam on the",
                " target, the size of the entrance collimator of the",
                " spectrometer, the coplanarity of the reaction plane",
                " with the the horizontal plane of the spectrometer,",
                " etc.) in the calculation of the integral (4%)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The deuteron photodisintegration  cross  sections have",
                " been measured at c.m.s.  angles of 90,  105, 120, and",
                " 135 degree and in the energy range 250 - 500 MeV. The",
                " experimental data   are   compared  with  theoretical",
                " calculations which take into account  the  excitation",
                " of the dibarion resonances."
              ]
            }
          ],
